data.title: Ross McClellan - Men's Lacrosse
data.meta_description: Ross McClellan (22) D  - 2017Started 13 of 14 matches as a junior defender … Third on the team with 17 caused turnovers and sixth with 23 ground balls …
data.text:
2017

Started 13 of 14 matches as a junior defender … Third on the team with 17 caused turnovers and sixth with 23 ground balls … Scored a goal against Oglethorpe (April 8) … Contributed an assist against Birmingham Southern (April 2) … Had six ground balls and four caused turnovers against Hanover (Feb. 25).

2016

Sophomore defender appeared in 11 games … Recorded five ground balls and three caused turnovers … Netted first collegiate goal at Oglethorpe (April 2).

2015

Played in 11 games as a rookie … Had nine ground balls and a pair of caused turnovers.

HIGH SCHOOL

Louisville, Ky., native played at Collegiate.
